Privacy and Cookie Policy
GAME HOLLYWOOD HONG KONG LIMITED, and its Affiliates, (Affiliate means, in relation to any person, any subsidiary or holding company of such person, any subsidiary of such person’s holding company, and any company in which such person or its holding company holds or is able to control, directly or indirectly, the voting rights of not less than 20% of the issued share capital. holding company and subsidiaries) (together as "GAME HOLLYWOOD"), is dedicated to protecting the privacy rights of its online users ("you" or "user"). Here Affiliates shall mean Now To Play Game Limited, registered number 1580619, address: 11/F, Tai Sang Bank Building, 784 Nathan Road, Kowloon, Hong Kong and Now to play game Sucursal en España, address:  C/Gran via de les corts catalanes 722 Ent 3ª 08013 Barcelona Spain. This Privacy and Cookie Policy has been crafted to inform you as to the ways GAME HOLLYWOOD collects, stores, uses, and manages the information you provide during the use of any GAME HOLLYWOOD games or application ("Service" or “Services”).
